		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Upcoming Wiki maintenance: 2015/03/15</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />This coming Sunday, <strong>2015/03/15 @ 1600 PDT (UTC-0700)</strong>, I will be upgrading our version of MediaWiki from 1.20.2 to 1.24.1.  Full backups of the database and all MediaWiki source will be done before hand, so that if the upgrade does not go well we can roll back without repercussions.<br /><br />I imagine this will take a couple hours (the upgrade should be quick, but testing things + updating any extensions we have may be tedious).  I will be available on IRC (EFnet, #nesdev, nick koitsu) if people have questions or concerns.  I don't know if Tepples will be around during that time, but if he is, he may also be able to shepherd questions.<br /><br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
