	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />1600 PDT = 4 PM US Pacific Daylight Time<br />1900 EDT = 7 PM US Eastern Daylight Time<br />2300 UTC = 11 PM Coordinated Universal Time<br /><br />Yes, I plan to be in #nesdev on EFnet at 19:00 EDT tomorrow night. I'll make my own HTML backup of the wiki before and after the maintenance, and afterward, I plan to release a new static HTML snapshot.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
