	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Upcoming Wiki maintenance: 2015/03/15</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Wiki upgrade has completed successfully.  It took longer than anticipated due to our mw1_objectcache table for MediaWiki being 1.2GB (clearing this took almost 25 minutes).  No issues were encountered.<br /><br />Users should note that the upgrade does change one default behaviour: any page you edit or create will be added to your &quot;watchlist&quot;.  You can change this default by logging in to the Wiki, clicking <strong>preferences</strong> in the upper right, then choose the <strong>Watchlist</strong> tab; refer to relevant checkboxes under <strong>Advanced</strong>.<br /><br />If you encounter any issues, please make a post in the <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewforum.php?f=16" class="postlink">nesdevWiki board</a> and we'll take care of it.<br /><br />Thank you!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
